1
00:01:31,100 --> 00:01:35,220
=The Tale of Rose=

2
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:39,140
=Episode 33=

3
00:01:43,340 --> 00:01:45,890
That day, I was drinking alcohol.

4
00:01:46,830 --> 00:01:47,840
Well,

5
00:01:49,420 --> 00:01:51,360
you want a kid,

6
00:01:51,630 --> 00:01:52,470
and...

7
00:01:55,940 --> 00:01:58,080
Do you prefer a boy or a girl?

8
00:02:00,990 --> 00:02:02,410
A boy.

9
00:02:03,470 --> 00:02:04,410
Boys are good.

10
00:03:06,140 --> 00:03:07,490
(No, no.)

11
00:03:36,860 --> 00:03:38,650
Daddy.

12
00:03:41,180 --> 00:03:42,110
Taichu,

13
00:03:42,110 --> 00:03:43,180
what are you doing?

14
00:03:43,180 --> 00:03:45,140
Making breakfast.

15
00:03:45,140 --> 00:03:46,250
Making breakfast?

16
00:03:49,140 --> 00:03:50,600
You cooked so much.

17
00:03:53,580 --> 00:03:55,040
Daddy, try it.

18
00:03:55,580 --> 00:03:56,420
Let me try it.

19
00:04:02,390 --> 00:04:03,230
So delicious.

20
00:04:03,350 --> 00:04:04,370
You're amazing.

21
00:04:06,020 --> 00:04:06,860
Taichu,

22
00:04:07,110 --> 00:04:08,530
you made so many servings.

23
00:04:09,620 --> 00:04:11,110
This one is Mommy's.

24
00:04:11,110 --> 00:04:13,020
This is Grandma's.

25
00:04:13,020 --> 00:04:14,560
This is Grandpa's.

26
00:04:14,830 --> 00:04:16,500
This is Uncle's.

27
00:04:16,500 --> 00:04:18,260
This is Auntie's.

28
00:04:18,260 --> 00:04:19,520
This one

29
00:04:19,910 --> 00:04:21,080
is for Nanny, right?

30
00:04:21,380 --> 00:04:23,000
This one is for Fu Jiaming.

31
00:04:31,500 --> 00:04:34,130
It's done. It's done.

32
00:04:36,150 --> 00:04:36,990
Taichu, does Mommy

33
00:04:37,710 --> 00:04:40,370
often take you to see Fu Jiaming?

34
00:04:41,060 --> 00:04:42,910
He's my good friend.

35
00:04:42,910 --> 00:04:44,230
When I go back,

36
00:04:44,230 --> 00:04:46,960
I want to give this to Fu Jiaming.

37
00:04:51,620 --> 00:04:52,460
Taichu,

38
00:04:54,150 --> 00:04:54,990
can you

39
00:04:55,420 --> 00:04:56,370
not go back to Beijing?

40
00:04:57,380 --> 00:04:59,960
Stay in Shanghai with me, okay?

41
00:05:01,630 --> 00:05:02,500
Why?

42
00:05:02,500 --> 00:05:05,470
Then I won't see Mommy,

43
00:05:05,470 --> 00:05:07,260
Grandma, Grandpa,

44
00:05:07,260 --> 00:05:08,710
Uncle, Auntie,

45
00:05:08,710 --> 00:05:11,490
Xini, Chun, Xuan,

46
00:05:12,470 --> 00:05:14,000
and Fu Jiaming.

47
00:05:20,470 --> 00:05:21,310
Taichu,

48
00:05:24,260 --> 00:05:25,100
your mom

49
00:05:26,740 --> 00:05:28,080
has Fu Jiaming.

50
00:05:29,420 --> 00:05:31,520
Grandma has Grandpa.

51
00:05:32,380 --> 00:05:33,810
Uncle has Auntie.

52
00:05:34,260 --> 00:05:35,440
They all have someone.

53
00:05:37,260 --> 00:05:38,810
But when you're not here,

54
00:05:39,590 --> 00:05:40,690
I have no one.

55
00:05:42,670 --> 00:05:43,730
In my heart,

56
00:05:44,710 --> 00:05:46,850
you're the most important.

57
00:05:48,470 --> 00:05:51,760
You're more important
than anyone or anything else.

58
00:05:54,550 --> 00:05:55,980
I want to be with you

59
00:05:55,980 --> 00:05:57,370
every second

60
00:05:57,990 --> 00:05:58,960
and make you happy.

61
00:06:11,710 --> 00:06:13,000
When you're not here,

62
00:06:14,710 --> 00:06:16,610
I really miss you.

63
00:06:18,620 --> 00:06:19,460
Taichu,

64
00:06:21,110 --> 00:06:22,080
live with me,

65
00:06:23,230 --> 00:06:24,080
okay?

66
00:06:27,940 --> 00:06:30,440
My house is bigger than Grandma's house,

67
00:06:31,150 --> 00:06:33,250
I will also buy you many toys.

68
00:06:34,300 --> 00:06:36,050
If you like playing the piano,

69
00:06:36,940 --> 00:06:38,320
I will buy you a piano

70
00:06:38,910 --> 00:06:41,290
and find a piano teacher, okay?

71
00:06:43,380 --> 00:06:44,220
Taichu,

72
00:06:46,150 --> 00:06:47,290
I only have you now.

73
00:06:55,670 --> 00:06:58,200
Daddy, don't cry.

74
00:07:44,380 --> 00:07:45,520
Don't get in the way.

75
00:07:45,740 --> 00:07:46,810
What are you looking at?

76
00:07:47,030 --> 00:07:48,050
Nothing.

77
00:08:08,550 --> 00:08:09,390
Lele.

78
00:08:10,060 --> 00:08:10,900
Lele.

79
00:08:11,710 --> 00:08:13,000
Do you still remember me?

80
00:08:13,620 --> 00:08:14,520
Hello, Uncle.

81
00:08:14,990 --> 00:08:15,830
Lele,

82
00:08:16,030 --> 00:08:16,960
how old are you?

83
00:08:17,230 --> 00:08:18,070
Five years old.

84
00:08:18,590 --> 00:08:19,880
You're so tall.

85
00:08:20,470 --> 00:08:21,760
Doesn't look like five.

86
00:08:22,380 --> 00:08:23,710
Are you actually six years old?

87
00:08:23,710 --> 00:08:25,560
- You remembered wrong.
- I'm five.

88
00:08:26,550 --> 00:08:27,390
Lele,

89
00:08:27,820 --> 00:08:28,660
go home now.

90
00:08:31,060 --> 00:08:31,900
Zhenhua?

91
00:08:32,990 --> 00:08:34,210
Came back to see your parents?

92
00:08:35,430 --> 00:08:36,900
I saw Lele just now,

93
00:08:36,900 --> 00:08:37,990
so I greeted him.

94
00:08:37,990 --> 00:08:39,610
This child is introverted.

95
00:08:39,760 --> 00:08:40,920
I was introverted when I was a child.

96
00:08:42,860 --> 00:08:45,070
They say sons look like their mothers.

97
00:08:45,070 --> 00:08:46,140
Your eyes are so big.

98
00:08:46,140 --> 00:08:48,570
His single eyelid must've taken after his dad.

99
00:08:50,020 --> 00:08:51,250
I don't have a dad.

100
00:08:56,260 --> 00:08:57,250
We should go home.

101
00:08:57,660 --> 00:08:58,500
Let's go, Lele.

102
00:08:59,540 --> 00:09:00,380
Goodbye.

103
00:09:00,430 --> 00:09:01,450
Goodbye, Uncle.

104
00:09:02,020 --> 00:09:02,860
Let's go.

105
00:09:18,990 --> 00:09:19,830
Hello.

106
00:09:20,230 --> 00:09:22,000
How's Taichu doing? Is she good?

107
00:09:22,780 --> 00:09:23,620
Very well-behaved.

108
00:09:23,910 --> 00:09:25,640
When is she coming back?
I'll pick her up at the airport.

109
00:09:28,070 --> 00:09:29,800
Withdraw Taichu from the Beijing kindergarten.

110
00:09:30,380 --> 00:09:32,210
I'll find a good one for her here.

111
00:09:34,740 --> 00:09:35,580
Why?

112
00:09:36,430 --> 00:09:37,270
In the future,

113
00:09:37,900 --> 00:09:39,330
she'll live in Shanghai with me.

114
00:09:41,380 --> 00:09:42,220
What?

115
00:09:43,260 --> 00:09:44,100
You...

116
00:09:45,590 --> 00:09:46,490
What do you mean?

117
00:09:49,350 --> 00:09:50,190
Huang Yimei,

118
00:09:50,900 --> 00:09:52,570
didn't I warn you

119
00:09:52,990 --> 00:09:55,370
not to let Fu Jiaming see my daughter?

120
00:09:56,110 --> 00:09:57,330
Did you listen to me?

121
00:09:58,110 --> 00:09:58,950
You...

122
00:09:59,230 --> 00:10:00,630
That didn't make any sense.

123
00:10:00,630 --> 00:10:01,570
Why should I listen?

124
00:10:02,310 --> 00:10:04,540
Now, her mind is full of Fu Jiaming.

125
00:10:04,540 --> 00:10:06,260
She's always thinking about him.

126
00:10:06,260 --> 00:10:07,130
In her heart,

127
00:10:07,500 --> 00:10:09,800
he is even more important than me.

128
00:10:10,590 --> 00:10:11,740
Didn't you teach her that?

129
00:10:11,740 --> 00:10:13,450
Don't be so petty, okay?

130
00:10:14,350 --> 00:10:16,680
Kids long for whoever's not around.

131
00:10:17,140 --> 00:10:19,140
When she was here, she always talked about you.

132
00:10:19,140 --> 00:10:20,490
You don't need to tell me these things.

133
00:10:21,310 --> 00:10:23,040
I think you haven't taught her well.

134
00:10:23,430 --> 00:10:24,450
Then I'll take over from now on.

135
00:10:25,070 --> 00:10:26,280
Taichu will stay with me.

136
00:10:26,620 --> 00:10:27,630
Fang Xiewen, let me tell you.

137
00:10:27,630 --> 00:10:28,490
Stop this.

138
00:10:28,830 --> 00:10:30,450
I have Taichu's custody.

139
00:10:30,950 --> 00:10:32,900
You can't decide to keep her in Shanghai.

140
00:10:32,900 --> 00:10:34,210
Why can't I?

141
00:10:34,470 --> 00:10:35,490
She's my daughter.

142
00:10:43,140 --> 00:10:44,180
(Fang Xiewen)

143
00:10:48,700 --> 00:10:50,180
(Rose)

144
00:10:54,700 --> 00:10:55,820
(Fang Xiewen)

145
00:11:13,860 --> 00:11:14,700
Hello?

146
00:11:15,230 --> 00:11:16,070
Uncle Bai,

147
00:11:16,230 --> 00:11:17,090
are you busy?

148
00:11:17,950 --> 00:11:18,790
Huang,

149
00:11:19,260 --> 00:11:20,430
I'm free.

150
00:11:20,430 --> 00:11:21,270
What's up?

151
00:11:22,540 --> 00:11:23,750
You're my major shareholder,

152
00:11:23,750 --> 00:11:25,780
so I need to update you

153
00:11:25,780 --> 00:11:27,000
from time to time about work.

154
00:11:28,380 --> 00:11:29,970
I trust you.

155
00:11:30,620 --> 00:11:32,610
No need for updates on daily work.

156
00:11:33,230 --> 00:11:34,070
Besides,

157
00:11:34,070 --> 00:11:35,880
don't I have someone handling finances for me?

158
00:11:38,660 --> 00:11:40,020
Oh, Uncle Bai,

159
00:11:40,020 --> 00:11:41,880
Xiaohe has returned.

160
00:11:43,020 --> 00:11:44,830
Yeah, she's back this year

161
00:11:44,830 --> 00:11:45,800
and has gone back to school.

162
00:11:46,590 --> 00:11:47,430
Why?

163
00:11:48,020 --> 00:11:49,400
Have you two met?

164
00:11:50,550 --> 00:11:51,940
We bumped into each other in the courtyard.

165
00:11:53,430 --> 00:11:54,330
Great.

166
00:11:56,110 --> 00:11:58,210
I see the kid has grown up.

167
00:11:58,710 --> 00:11:59,550
Well.

168
00:11:59,830 --> 00:12:01,570
What does her husband do?

169
00:12:03,540 --> 00:12:04,760
Well...

170
00:12:10,260 --> 00:12:12,760
You two can talk about that when you meet.

171
00:12:14,900 --> 00:12:15,850
Okay.

172
00:12:16,260 --> 00:12:18,780
Uncle Bai, it's nothing.

173
00:12:18,780 --> 00:12:20,370
I'll come to see you.

174
00:12:20,740 --> 00:12:21,580
Talk to you later.

175
00:12:22,990 --> 00:12:23,830
Goodbye.

176
00:12:26,020 --> 00:12:27,680
He let us talk ourselves?

177
00:12:37,700 --> 00:12:39,140
(Bai Xiaohe)

178
00:12:49,980 --> 00:12:52,300
(Rose)

179
00:12:53,380 --> 00:12:54,610
Rose, what's wrong?

180
00:12:55,020 --> 00:12:55,860
Zhenhua,

181
00:12:56,070 --> 00:12:57,640
Fang Xiewen called me.

182
00:12:57,900 --> 00:13:00,160
He told me to cancel the kindergarten here.

183
00:13:00,590 --> 00:13:01,640
He won't let Taichu come back.

184
00:13:02,500 --> 00:13:03,340
What?

185
00:13:03,990 --> 00:13:04,830
Where are you?

186
00:13:04,830 --> 00:13:05,920
I'm on my way home.

187
00:13:07,620 --> 00:13:08,730
Wait for me. I'll be there soon.

188
00:13:25,950 --> 00:13:26,880
Still can't reach him?

189
00:13:27,500 --> 00:13:28,400
He's not answering calls.

190
00:13:28,660 --> 00:13:29,850
The company can't find him.

191
00:13:30,070 --> 00:13:31,150
What a jerk.

192
00:13:31,150 --> 00:13:32,730
Taking the child to Shanghai.

193
00:13:33,020 --> 00:13:34,110
It's not deceiving, right?

194
00:13:34,110 --> 00:13:35,280
Isn't it more like kidnapping?

195
00:13:35,500 --> 00:13:36,680
Let's call the police.

196
00:13:39,310 --> 00:13:40,880
No, I have to go there.

197
00:13:41,350 --> 00:13:43,020
Don't tell Dad and Mom for now, okay?

198
00:13:43,020 --> 00:13:43,860
Anyway,

199
00:13:43,860 --> 00:13:45,520
find a way to stall for a couple of days.

200
00:13:45,830 --> 00:13:46,670
No, no, no.

201
00:13:46,950 --> 00:13:48,730
Rose, let me go.

202
00:13:49,230 --> 00:13:51,260
I can't give birth,
but I can fight for the child.

203
00:13:51,260 --> 00:13:53,160
With Fu Jiaming like this, you can't leave.

204
00:13:53,380 --> 00:13:55,000
Taichu is my daughter.

205
00:13:55,260 --> 00:13:56,940
But if this escalates,

206
00:13:56,940 --> 00:13:57,940
what should Taichu do?

207
00:13:57,940 --> 00:13:59,740
Will she have to choose between Mom and Dad?

208
00:13:59,740 --> 00:14:01,040
I can't think of that.

209
00:14:01,430 --> 00:14:03,250
You know what Fang is like.

210
00:14:03,710 --> 00:14:05,040
He's now holding Taichu,

211
00:14:05,500 --> 00:14:08,400
just like he controlled me back then.

212
00:14:09,780 --> 00:14:10,700
No, no. I have to go to Shanghai.

213
00:14:10,700 --> 00:14:12,450
Rose, calm down.

214
00:14:13,190 --> 00:14:15,800
Dad often says many historical events
stem from impulsive actions.

215
00:14:16,030 --> 00:14:16,900
Think about it.

216
00:14:16,900 --> 00:14:19,180
What does it mean for Fang to hold Taichu?

217
00:14:19,180 --> 00:14:20,830
He's trying to make you go to Shanghai.

218
00:14:20,830 --> 00:14:22,230
He wants to provoke you face-to-face.

219
00:14:22,230 --> 00:14:24,250
Once you fall out, there's no turning back.

220
00:14:27,470 --> 00:14:28,470
You're too involved to see this.

221
00:14:28,470 --> 00:14:29,730
Leave this to me.

222
00:14:30,190 --> 00:14:31,830
Send me his address.

223
00:14:31,830 --> 00:14:32,680
I'll go right now.

224
00:14:32,690 --> 00:14:33,850
If there's a problem, I'll call you.

225
00:14:34,710 --> 00:14:35,680
Don't worry.

226
00:14:36,020 --> 00:14:36,860
I'm going.

227
00:14:50,140 --> 00:14:50,980
Hello, Mr. Fang.

228
00:14:52,780 --> 00:14:54,400
Mr. Fang, that person is here again.

229
00:14:56,430 --> 00:14:57,450
Mr. Fang is here.

230
00:15:00,470 --> 00:15:02,140
Ran away fast yesterday.

231
00:15:02,140 --> 00:15:04,830
Looks like you've done
plenty of shady business.

232
00:15:04,830 --> 00:15:06,040
Skilled at dodging.

233
00:15:06,860 --> 00:15:07,700
By the way,

234
00:15:07,860 --> 00:15:09,230
your staff here are quite good,

235
00:15:09,230 --> 00:15:10,400
loyal to you.

236
00:15:10,900 --> 00:15:11,870
Not a single person told me

237
00:15:11,870 --> 00:15:13,310
where you're living now.

238
00:15:13,310 --> 00:15:15,490
For this, you should give them a raise.

239
00:15:16,430 --> 00:15:18,370
- The boss should...
- Don't chat here with me.

240
00:15:19,660 --> 00:15:20,640
Let Huang Yimei come over

241
00:15:21,070 --> 00:15:22,920
to talk about the custody again.

242
00:15:23,190 --> 00:15:24,150
Rose has handed this matter

243
00:15:24,150 --> 00:15:25,780
over to me.

244
00:15:25,780 --> 00:15:27,630
If you don't let me see the child,

245
00:15:27,630 --> 00:15:29,250
I'll have to keep stalling here.

246
00:15:29,860 --> 00:15:31,030
Anyway, with my laptop,

247
00:15:31,030 --> 00:15:32,880
I can handle remote work.

248
00:15:43,660 --> 00:15:44,500
You...

249
00:15:45,470 --> 00:15:46,880
The coffee you made for me yesterday

250
00:15:47,140 --> 00:15:48,850
was good. Make me another cup.

251
00:15:54,540 --> 00:15:55,380
Please.

252
00:16:01,540 --> 00:16:02,500
Then get back to work.

253
00:16:02,500 --> 00:16:04,090
Later, I'll ask your boss to give you a raise.

254
00:16:08,020 --> 00:16:08,860
I've met him.

255
00:16:09,350 --> 00:16:10,210
The talk went well.

256
00:16:10,780 --> 00:16:13,370
He said he'll consider it.

257
00:16:13,990 --> 00:16:15,950
In a few days,

258
00:16:15,950 --> 00:16:17,680
I should be able to bring Taichu back.

259
00:16:18,070 --> 00:16:18,910
Zhou.

260
00:16:18,990 --> 00:16:20,900
Don't worry. Take good care of Jiaming.

261
00:16:20,900 --> 00:16:23,070
Finish up the engine part of this game.

262
00:16:23,070 --> 00:16:24,390
Okay. Bye now.

263
00:16:24,390 --> 00:16:25,500
Refine it further.

264
00:16:25,500 --> 00:16:26,340
Sure.

265
00:16:30,860 --> 00:16:31,700
Right.

266
00:16:32,230 --> 00:16:33,070
Okay.

267
00:16:36,110 --> 00:16:37,090
Good.

268
00:16:39,350 --> 00:16:40,210
Mr. Fang,

269
00:16:40,950 --> 00:16:42,330
since everyone's here,

270
00:16:42,540 --> 00:16:44,310
would you like to share with everyone

271
00:16:44,310 --> 00:16:45,700
how you managed to deceive my niece

272
00:16:45,700 --> 00:16:46,850
into coming to Shanghai?

273
00:16:47,470 --> 00:16:48,870
Mr. Fang, today, a client

274
00:16:48,870 --> 00:16:50,850
wants to visit our server room
and operations office.

275
00:16:51,780 --> 00:16:53,520
If he's around,

276
00:16:54,190 --> 00:16:55,030
then...

277
00:16:55,190 --> 00:16:56,030
I see.

278
00:16:57,710 --> 00:16:58,550
Go on.

279
00:17:04,230 --> 00:17:05,480
I'll call the police.

280
00:17:06,020 --> 00:17:07,020
Call the police?

281
00:17:07,020 --> 00:17:07,960
Sure.

282
00:17:08,230 --> 00:17:09,240
I want to call the police too.

283
00:17:09,670 --> 00:17:10,950
My niece has gone missing.

284
00:17:10,950 --> 00:17:13,200
I have evidence that you kidnapped her.

285
00:17:13,870 --> 00:17:15,610
If this big boss were arrested,

286
00:17:16,150 --> 00:17:17,910
can the company still function?

287
00:17:17,910 --> 00:17:19,160
She's my daughter.

288
00:17:19,390 --> 00:17:21,060
It's natural for her to live with me.

289
00:17:21,060 --> 00:17:22,370
Let me tell you one last time.

290
00:17:22,950 --> 00:17:24,060
