00:31:11,510 --> 00:31:12,770
I've been ready for a long time.

578
00:31:12,990 --> 00:31:14,190
Let's not wait until next month.

579
00:31:14,190 --> 00:31:15,300
Let's try today.

580
00:31:15,300 --> 00:31:17,060
No. Ovulation is in two days.

581
00:31:17,060 --> 00:31:18,030
It won't make a difference.

582
00:31:18,030 --> 00:31:19,580
Stop it, stop it.

583
00:31:19,580 --> 00:31:22,200
Hold on for better quality.

584
00:31:24,950 --> 00:31:25,790
Don't move.

585
00:31:26,950 --> 00:31:28,240
Wait until you're calm.

586
00:31:44,630 --> 00:31:46,530
Oh, my god.

587
00:32:12,390 --> 00:32:13,770
(Liu Zhiming)
In Beijing, there's Doctor Yao,

588
00:32:14,060 --> 00:32:17,090
one of the top cardiac specialists in China.

589
00:32:17,340 --> 00:32:18,880
It's hard to get an appointment with him.

590
00:32:19,780 --> 00:32:21,050
I've already asked this friend

591
00:32:21,260 --> 00:32:22,330
to arrange it for you.

592
00:32:22,950 --> 00:32:24,850
When you get back, call him.

593
00:32:25,060 --> 00:32:27,230
He'll arrange everything for you.

594
00:32:27,230 --> 00:32:28,130
Set a time.

595
00:32:28,540 --> 00:32:31,480
Go to the hospital and find Doctor Yao.

596
00:32:32,680 --> 00:32:33,540
I heard

597
00:32:33,540 --> 00:32:36,400
Doctor Yao is going abroad next week,

598
00:32:36,630 --> 00:32:37,720
and he's only available this week.

599
00:32:38,340 --> 00:32:39,640
Contact him as soon as possible.

600
00:32:39,990 --> 00:32:41,400
Take your boyfriend to see him.

601
00:32:43,580 --> 00:32:44,610
Why are you helping him?

602
00:32:47,340 --> 00:32:49,810
Helping him is helping you, isn't it?

603
00:32:50,190 --> 00:32:51,130
Helping you

604
00:32:51,580 --> 00:32:52,850
is helping my daughter, right?

605
00:32:53,260 --> 00:32:55,190
Since I have these connections,

606
00:32:55,190 --> 00:32:56,030
why not use them?

607
00:33:02,630 --> 00:33:03,500
Unexpectedly...

608
00:33:03,500 --> 00:33:05,640
Unexpectedly, I'd be so righteous.

609
00:33:06,630 --> 00:33:07,470
Right?

610
00:33:11,020 --> 00:33:11,860
Seriously,

611
00:33:12,870 --> 00:33:13,720
I'm sorry

612
00:33:14,340 --> 00:33:15,640
for always causing you trouble.

613
00:33:17,230 --> 00:33:19,290
Consider it making up

614
00:33:20,230 --> 00:33:21,240
for past mistakes.

615
00:33:34,100 --> 00:33:34,960
Thank you.

616
00:34:26,750 --> 00:34:27,590
Jiaming.

617
00:34:30,620 --> 00:34:31,460
You're back.

618
00:34:33,870 --> 00:34:35,280
There's something I need to discuss with you.

619
00:34:45,260 --> 00:34:47,580
(Bai Xiaohe)

620
00:34:50,260 --> 00:34:56,860
(Bai Xiaohe)

621
00:34:56,860 --> 00:34:57,900
(May 8, 2013)

622
00:35:04,470 --> 00:35:06,720
May 8th.

623
00:35:09,910 --> 00:35:12,090
We did it

624
00:35:13,540 --> 00:35:15,010
in September

625
00:35:15,500 --> 00:35:16,720
or October.

626
00:35:19,750 --> 00:35:21,760
So it should be June. Not right.

627
00:35:23,870 --> 00:35:26,320
Could have been premature.

628
00:35:38,900 --> 00:35:40,700
(Huang Zhenhua: Forgive me for asking.
Are you divorced?)

629
00:35:50,300 --> 00:35:52,180
(Bai Xiaohe: I'm single.)

630
00:35:54,430 --> 00:35:56,490
What answer is that?

631
00:36:06,090 --> 00:36:07,050
What are you muttering about?

632
00:36:09,470 --> 00:36:10,310
Do you need something?

633
00:36:11,020 --> 00:36:11,860
Nothing.

634
00:36:12,310 --> 00:36:14,130
I've made an appointment for tomorrow.

635
00:36:16,020 --> 00:36:17,130
I'll go with you.

636
00:36:20,350 --> 00:36:21,570
Thank your friend for me.

637
00:36:22,910 --> 00:36:23,760
This disease

638
00:36:24,580 --> 00:36:25,680
has been with me my whole life.

639
00:36:26,950 --> 00:36:28,720
Every doctor says pretty much the same thing.

640
00:36:29,390 --> 00:36:31,840
Doctor Yao is the best cardiac doctor in China.

641
00:36:33,270 --> 00:36:35,130
Maybe he can find a way to cure you completely.

642
00:36:40,430 --> 00:36:41,530
Do you want me to go?

643
00:36:47,580 --> 00:36:49,930
You said you wanted to live
like a normal person,

644
00:36:50,660 --> 00:36:52,130
to be my normal boyfriend.

645
00:36:53,950 --> 00:36:55,200
I think this is a chance.

646
00:37:02,430 --> 00:37:03,270
I understand.

647
00:37:05,180 --> 00:37:06,020
I'll go.

648
00:37:19,660 --> 00:37:20,970
Does he look like me?

649
00:37:24,060 --> 00:37:24,900
Look at the eyes.

650
00:37:25,790 --> 00:37:26,890
Single eyelid, small eyes.

651
00:37:27,270 --> 00:37:30,020
Does his mouth look like Bai Xiaohe's?

652
00:37:30,020 --> 00:37:31,160
The nose looks like Bai Xiaohe's too.

653
00:37:31,700 --> 00:37:33,360
Aren't those our genes?

654
00:37:33,580 --> 00:37:36,050
Do this pose.

655
00:37:45,100 --> 00:37:46,790
But she didn't say anything.

656
00:37:46,790 --> 00:37:48,800
How do you know he's yours?

657
00:37:49,660 --> 00:37:50,930
She didn't say anything,

658
00:37:51,140 --> 00:37:53,430
but why does she always evade questions

659
00:37:53,430 --> 00:37:54,610
about the child's father?

660
00:37:55,350 --> 00:37:56,490
Doesn't that seem suspicious?

661
00:37:58,660 --> 00:38:00,640
How can you not remember anything

662
00:38:01,220 --> 00:38:03,570
about such a big event?

663
00:38:09,310 --> 00:38:11,010
Do you think it's possible

664
00:38:11,430 --> 00:38:15,680
that she did something to your drink?

665
00:38:24,220 --> 00:38:25,640
She studied chemistry.

666
00:38:29,990 --> 00:38:30,970
No, no, no.

667
00:38:33,220 --> 00:38:35,890
If the child is yours,

668
00:38:36,180 --> 00:38:37,640
what will you do?

669
00:38:50,390 --> 00:38:51,230
How about this?

670
00:38:51,950 --> 00:38:55,020
Let's start with a detailed examination.

671
00:38:55,020 --> 00:38:56,570
After the results come out,

672
00:38:57,060 --> 00:38:59,410
we will discuss the treatment plan.

673
00:39:00,060 --> 00:39:00,900
Alright?

674
00:39:01,500 --> 00:39:02,340
Thank you.

675
00:39:02,540 --> 00:39:03,380
Okay.

676
00:40:16,180 --> 00:40:17,640
These are the images you provided

677
00:40:18,220 --> 00:40:22,050
from the last surgery and CT scan.

678
00:40:22,620 --> 00:40:23,840
These are from this time.

679
00:40:24,180 --> 00:40:27,130
Comparing them, you can clearly see

680
00:40:28,310 --> 00:40:29,970
the severe damage

681
00:40:30,580 --> 00:40:31,420
to the left ventricle

682
00:40:31,950 --> 00:40:33,890
and adhesions at the site

683
00:40:34,750 --> 00:40:36,050
of the previous surgery.

684
00:40:36,950 --> 00:40:38,490
Currently,

685
00:40:39,870 --> 00:40:41,720
surgery is no longer feasible.

686
00:40:42,540 --> 00:40:44,200
Are you saying he can't have surgery?

687
00:40:45,870 --> 00:40:47,010
The chance of success

688
00:40:47,430 --> 00:40:48,320
is very low.

689
00:40:48,830 --> 00:40:49,720
I don't recommend it.

690
00:40:50,180 --> 00:40:52,390
I believe no doctor in China

691
00:40:52,390 --> 00:40:54,970
would dare to operate on him either.

692
00:40:55,660 --> 00:40:57,680
Even with foreign equipment,

693
00:40:57,950 --> 00:41:00,130
I'm afraid we can't guarantee it.

694
00:41:00,390 --> 00:41:01,230
Then...

695
00:41:02,350 --> 00:41:03,490
Then how can we treat him?

696
00:41:04,750 --> 00:41:07,450
There's no use doing that.

697
00:41:07,660 --> 00:41:08,500
You should

698
00:41:09,140 --> 00:41:11,200
prepare for the worst.

699
00:41:26,910 --> 00:41:27,750
Doctor,

700
00:41:30,870 --> 00:41:31,840
how much time does he have?

701
00:41:33,220 --> 00:41:34,200
Not optimistic.

702
00:41:36,060 --> 00:41:36,900
Six months?

703
00:41:39,990 --> 00:41:41,280
Sorry.

704
00:41:42,910 --> 00:41:43,800
Three months?

705
00:41:46,020 --> 00:41:46,890
Anytime.

706
00:41:47,620 --> 00:41:49,160
What you can do now

707
00:41:49,470 --> 00:41:50,530
is try to minimize

708
00:41:51,350 --> 00:41:52,760
any regrets for him.

709
00:42:31,830 --> 00:42:32,670
Jiaming,

710
00:42:33,350 --> 00:42:34,200
I'm back.

711
00:42:48,060 --> 00:42:48,900
Jiaming?

